dct_description_sm: Denmark. Geodaetisk Institut. Map notes locations of all branchs of Aktieselskabet Kjøbenhavns Handelsbank in Copenhagen. Municipal boundaries and postal district boundaries are shown. Bus routes are indicated. Verso: maps of Stroget ' Copenhagen's pedestrian street, and regional raillines, not to scale. "With the compliments of Aktieselskabet Kjøbenhavns Handelsbank.". 1962
